entry.string: Paypal Set-Up will set-up the necessary variables for use with the PayPal merchant tools such as the cart, pay now buttons, subscriptions. This module just sets up the defaults. To use the individual buttons and functionality, Dynamic Data must be hooked to your displays.
entry.translation: Peypel Set-Up veell set-up zee necessery fereeebles fur use-a veet zee PeyPel merchunt tuuls sooch es zee cert, pey noo boottuns, soobscreepshuns. Thees mudoole-a joost sets up zee deffoolts. Tu use-a zee indeefidooel boottuns und fooncshuneleety, Dynemeec Deta moost be-a huuked tu yuoor deespleys. Um gesh dee bork, bork!

entry.string: From the menu, you have one choice.
entry.translation: Frum zee menoo, yuoo hefe-a oone-a chueece-a.

entry.string: "Modify Configuration". From this menu option, you can update the necessary configuration options, such as your paypal account, and prefered currency.
entry.translation: "Mudeeffy Cunffeegooreshun". Frum thees menoo oopshun, yuoo cun updete-a zee necessery cunffeegooreshun oopshuns, sooch es yuoor peypel eccuoont, und preffered coorrency. Bork bork bork!

entry.string: There are no blocks included at this time.
entry.translation: Zeere-a ere-a nu blucks inclooded et thees teeme-a.

entry.string: There are no hooks included at this time.
entry.translation: Zeere-a ere-a nu huuks inclooded et thees teeme-a.
